Nokutarisa kuna Mwari, kutarisa pana Mwari, uye kufungisisa nezve Shoko.

0:05:19.340,0:05:22.560
Tinofungisisa sei nezve Shoko?

0:05:22.560,0:05:33.540
Kana ndichiti, "Paunofunga zvakanyanya ..." Ndiri kutaura nezvekufungisisa - zvinopfuura kungofunga.

0:05:33.540,0:05:41.320
Kana ndichiti, "Paunofunga zvakanyanya ..." hazvisisiri pamusoro pemamiriro ezvinhu ako - asi pana Mwari.

0:05:41.320,0:05:48.600
Kana iwe uchifunga nezve zvaunoverenga, zvaunoona zvakakupoteredza, zvaunonzwa,

0:05:48.600,0:05:55.020
ndipo paunonyanya kuziva izwi rake.

0:05:55.020,0:05:56.360
Cherechedza izvozvo.

0:05:56.360,0:06:02.840
Kana ndichiti, "Paunonyanya kufunga ..." Ndinoreva kufungisisa.

0:06:02.840,0:06:05.080
Paunonyanya kufunga ..." Ndinoreva kufungisisa.

0:06:05.080,0:06:11.720
Usati wasvika pakufungisisa unofanirwa kupfuura nemuku "funga, funga, funga ..."

0:06:11.720,0:06:18.520
Ndiko kufungisisa - "funga, funga, funga ..."

0:06:18.520,0:06:29.700
Kwete kufunga - mamiriro ezvinhu, funga zvakare - hazvisisiri mamiriro ako - kuna Mwari.

0:06:29.700,0:06:42.820
Kutenda kunouya kwega pakarepo, ndiko kuti, sezva zvinofanirwa.

0:06:42.820,0:06:50.160
Ichi ndicho chikonzero nei usingagoni kuva nekutenda kana iwe uchiverenga Bhaibheri rako nenzira yaunoverenga mabhuku.

0:06:50.160,0:06:56.160
Kana uchiverenga Bhaibheri rako nenzira yaunoverenga nayo chemistry kana physics, iwe haugoni kuva nekutenda

0:06:56.160,0:07:02.700
nokuti kutenda kunouya kwega pakarepo.

0:07:02.700,0:07:09.520
Ichi ndicho chikonzero iwe usingagoni kuva nekutenda kana iwe uchichengeta izvo zvaunenge waverenga mundangariro.

0:07:09.520,0:07:13.400
Iwe unodhoma Bhaibheri rako.

0:07:13.400,0:07:23.780
Zvakanaka kuchengeta mundangariro, zvinokosha asi zvinofanirwa kuve zvinhu zvakakosha kwauri.

0:07:23.780,0:07:28.180
Zvakanaka kuchengeta mundangariro.

0:07:28.180,0:07:34.560
Kana uchiyeuka Bhaibheri mundangariro, zvakafanana nekuchengeta mvura mumukanwa mako.

0:07:34.560,0:07:45.940
Apo unoda kunwa uye iwe unochengetedza mvura mukanwa mako usingaimedze, kutambisa.

0:07:45.940,0:07:51.920
Kana mvura ikaramba iri mukanwa mako usingaimedze, kutambisa.

0:07:51.920,0:07:58.300
Muchiitiko chimwe chete, kana iwe uchiyeuka Bhaibheri mundangariro usingaribvumire kuti rive mukurarama kwako.

0:07:58.300,0:08:02.680
kuti rive chikamu chinokosha mauri, ikoko kutambisa.

0:08:02.680,0:08:05.620
Iwe unoverenga Bhaibheri rako, wotanga kuchengeta ndima mundangariro.

0:08:05.620,0:08:14.220
Tinochengeta Bhabheri redu mundangariro kuti tiriparidze, tiridzidzise, kwete kurirara.

0:08:14.220,0:08:22.180
Asi kurarama Bhaibheri ndiko kubvumira izvi kuti zvive zvinokosha kwatiri.

0:08:22.180,0:08:29.540
Kutenda kunobva kuna Mwari.

0:08:29.540,0:08:31.660
Kunobva kuna ani?

0:08:31.660,0:08:32.580
[Mwari.]

0:08:32.580,0:08:34.840
Mwari.

0:08:34.840,0:08:39.880
Harubvi kwatiri.

0:08:39.880,0:08:47.600
Ndicho chikonzero apo iwe unotarisa tarisa, pauri pachako, kwose kwose; haugoni kuwana rutendo.

0:08:47.600,0:08:54.540
Iwe unotarisa tarisa, kwauri pachako; haugoni kuwana rutendo.

0:08:54.540,0:09:00.740
Paunozoziva kuti Mwari akavimbika, kutenda kunouya.

0:09:00.740,0:09:07.760
Ah! Mwari mukuru! Zvinounza kutenda.

0:09:07.760,0:09:09.580
"Mukana we kutenda".

0:09:09.580,0:09:16.660
O, izvi zvakaitika sei? O, Mwari mukuru!

0:09:16.660,0:09:25.040
Zvinoreva kuti Mwari akavimbika - Anokupa mukana wo kutenda.

0:09:25.040,0:09:30.520
Iwe unotanga kuve ne kutenda uku uye kunotanga kukura zvakanyanya.

0:09:30.520,0:09:38.800
Imwe nguva; "O, ndapodzwa, kubwinya ngakuve kuna Mwari, ndi Mwari chete."

0:09:38.800,0:09:40.800
Umwe mukana wekutenda.

0:09:40.800,0:09:43.600
Kutenda kwako kuri kuwedzera zvishoma nezvishoma.

0:09:43.600,0:09:46.180
Kunouya kwega pakarepo.

0:09:46.180,0:09:54.160
Ichi ndicho chikonzero vadzidzisi vezvebhaibheri, vanyori vakawanda vanonyora nezve Bhaibheri - havana kutenda.

0:09:54.160,0:09:58.860
Vanyori vemabhuku akawanda pamusoro pezve Bhaibheri havana kutenda.

0:09:58.860,0:10:07.780
Vakadzidza kwazvo, ivo vanyori asi havana kutenda.

0:10:07.780,0:10:13.240
