0:10:43.580,0:10:53.980
Hungu, kuti iwe unoziva Jesu, iwe unoparidza Jesu uye vanhu vanokuona kuti iwe uri muparidzi anogona;

0:10:53.980,0:10:57.140
hazvirevi kuti une kutenda.

0:10:57.140,0:11:01.220
... kusvikira Jesu akuziva iwe.

0:11:01.220,0:11:11.160
Jesu anogona chete kutiziva isu no rutendo rwake, kwete ne kutenda kwedu; nokuteerera Kwake, kwete nekuteerera kwedu;

0:11:11.160,0:11:14.480
nokuzvininipisa Kwake, kwete nekuzvininipisa kwedu.

0:11:14.480,0:11:19.840
Unoona vanhu vanozvininipisa zvikuru uye vakareruka, asi hazvisi zva Mwari.

0:11:19.840,0:11:30.060
Unogona kuona vanhu vakatendeka kwazvo kwauri, asi hazvibve kuna Mwari.

0:11:30.060,0:11:39.020
Vanhu vanogona kuteerera kwazvo, kwauri - hongu, uyu mwana anoteerera - asi zvisingabve kuna Mwari.

0:11:39.020,0:11:46.120
Bhaibheri rakati, "Izvi zvandakakupa, kwete sekupa kunoita nyika ".

0:11:46.120,0:11:53.760
Zvose zvakapiwa na Jesu, nyika inogonawo kupa zvakafanana asi nemitemo.

0:11:53.760,0:11:59.220
Kana iwe ukasazvitarisisa zvakanaka kwazvo unogona kutadza kuziva mutsauko.

0:11:59.220,0:12:04.460
Ichi ndicho chikonzero nhasi isu tisingazivi mutsauko pakati peizvi neizvo.

0:12:04.460,0:12:09.380
Pane zvinhu zve Mweya, isu hatizivi.

0:12:09.380,0:12:16.960
"Izvozvi ndakakupa, kwete sezvo nyika inovapa" zvinoreva kuti zvose izvo Jesu ari kupa,

0:12:16.960,0:12:25.880
nyika inogona kupawo zvakare, asi nemusiyano.

0:12:25.880,0:12:27.020
Mutsauko wacho ndeupi?

0:12:27.020,0:12:32.020
Musiyano wacho magumo acho.

0:12:32.020,0:12:42.060
Kutanga kunogona kuoneka zvakafanana, pakati panogona kuita sepakafanana, asi magumo anogara akasiyana.

0:12:42.060,0:12:45.860
Magumo anoratidza musiyano.

0:12:45.860,0:12:53.840
Kutanga kunooneka se zvakafanana, unogona nekusaziva kusaona mutsauko.

0:12:53.840,0:13:01.500
Pakati - panguva imwechete iwe unogona kutadza kuziva mutsauko, nokuti tagumirwa.

0:13:01.500,0:13:04.660
Nokuda kwekupererwa kwedu hatizivi mutsauko.

0:13:04.660,0:13:12.060
Kupererwa kuti tive izvi, izvo, kuti tisvike ipapo - hatina mhosva kuti zvinouya sei, kuti zvinoratidzika sei,

0:13:12.060,0:13:15.760
sezvo akakupa chinhu chakafanana.

0:13:15.760,0:13:21.180
Kana magumo ezvauri kuita asingazove akanaka - hazvina maturo.

0:13:21.180,0:13:25.720
Zviri nani kuti usazviita zvachose.

0:13:25.720,0:13:29.540
Takaona kuguma kwevakawanda.

0:13:29.540,0:13:43.020
Kutanga - budiriro, pakati panoita sepane budiriro, asi kuguma - kuchema, kubowa kusuwa.

0:13:43.020,0:13:51.820
Magumo edu haafaniri kuguma apo patinopfuurira kuenda kune kubwinya.

0:13:51.820,0:13:57.240
