0:14:05.920,0:14:14.000
Asi kana pasina rekodhi apo rwendo runopera ne rekodhi yako inopera - kukosha kwazvo ndekwei....?

0:14:14.000,0:14:23.360
Dai kushingaira kwese kwe vapositori kwakaguma panguva yavo, vanhu vakaita seni vangadai vasipo nhasi.

0:14:23.360,0:14:26.340
Vakabhadhara mutengo mukuru wokuunza Vhangeri.

0:14:26.340,0:14:31.380
Nokuti Vhangeri harina kuguma panguva yavo, pakupera kwe rwendo rwavo -

0:14:31.380,0:14:37.640
Ichi ndicho chikonzero vanhu vakaita seni vachiri pano nhasi kuparidza Vhangeri.

0:14:37.640,0:14:49.240
