0:15:29.280,0:15:34.700
Sezvakangoita kune vapositori - isu tiri vana vasati vaberekwa panguva yavo.

0:15:34.700,0:15:40.900
Nhasi tiri kuonekwa, tiri kunakidzwa nemutengo wavakabhadhara.

0:15:40.900,0:15:45.340
Izwi rokuti "kutenda" ndiro ratisvitsa pane izvi.

0:15:45.340,0:15:48.520
Kutenda kunouya kwega pakarepo.

0:15:48.520,0:15:57.140
Harisi basa rokuverenga, kururama, kutikitira kana chero chipi nechipi chawakaita

0:15:57.140,0:16:02.040
zvinounza kutenda - kunouya kwega pakarepo, zvazvinofanirwa.

0:16:02.040,0:16:12.940
Ichi ndicho chikonzero usingagoni kuwana rutendo urworwo kana uchiverenga Bhaibheri rako nenzira yaunoverenga nayo mabhuku.

0:16:12.940,0:16:21.080
Ichi ndicho chikonzero zvakaoma kuti mumwe munhu ave nokutenda mushure mekupedza chikoro chebhaibheri.

0:16:21.080,0:16:24.780
Zvakaoma zvikuru.

0:16:24.780,0:16:31.620
Iwe unowana ruzivo irworwo, asi kutenda ikoko kunogara kwakaoma kuwana.

0:16:31.620,0:16:39.440
Kana uchiverenga Bhaibheri rako nenzira yaunoverenga nayo mabhuku haugoni kuwana rutendo rwatiri kutaura nezvarwo.

0:16:39.440,0:16:50.120
Nokuti, sezvandambo taura, chatinoti rutendo chimwe chinhu chine rukwaniso

0:16:50.120,0:16:55.840
rwekuumba simba remweya mukati memwoyo yedu.

0:16:55.840,0:16:57.920
Izvo zvinopfuura kungoverenga kwe mazuva ose.

0:16:57.920,0:17:01.160
Kunofanira kuve kuverenga kune kuzvipira.

