0:17:04.060,0:17:04.900
Nokuzvipira.

0:17:04.900,0:17:14.860
Udza waugere naye, "Zvinodarika kuverenga kwemazuva ose - kunofanira kuve kuverenga kune kuzvipira."

0:17:14.860,0:17:16.740
